## Monitoring & Management

### Command Line

```bash
# View queue status
rails solid_queue:status

# View jobs in queue
rails solid_queue:jobs

# View failed jobs
rails solid_queue:failed

# Retry failed jobs
rails solid_queue:retry_all

# Clear failed jobs
rails solid_queue:clear_failed
```

### Rails Console

```ruby
# View pending jobs
SolidQueue::Job.pending.count

# View failed jobs
SolidQueue::Job.failed.count

# View jobs by queue
SolidQueue::Job.where(queue_name: 'default').count

# Manually enqueue job
ArticleNotificationJob.perform_later(article.id)

# Perform job immediately (for testing)
ArticleNotificationJob.perform_now(article.id)
```

